echo -e "|${GRAY}1${NC}| OPENVPN ‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏ô‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏Ñ‡∏≠‡∏ô‡∏ü‡∏¥‡∏Å"
echo -e "|${GRAY}2${NC}| OPENVPN ‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏°‡∏π‡∏•‡πÄ‡∏ã‡∏¥‡∏ü‡πÄ‡∏ß‡∏≠‡∏£‡πå"
echo -e "|${GRAY}3${NC}| SQUID PROXY ‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå‡∏£‡∏≤‡∏¢‡∏•‡∏∞‡πÄ‡∏≠‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏î‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏û‡∏£‡πá‡∏≠‡∏Å‡∏ã‡∏µ‡πà"
echo -e "|${GRAY}4${NC}| MENU ‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå‡∏™‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏¥‡∏õ‡∏ó‡πå‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á‡πÄ‡∏°‡∏ô‡∏π"
echo ""
echo ""
read -p "‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏Å‡∏´‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏á‡∏≤‡∏ô : " EDIT

case $EDIT in

	1)
nano /etc/openvpn/client-common.txt
exit
	;;
	2)
nano /etc/openvpn/server.conf
exit
	;;
	3)
if [[ "$VERSION_ID" = 'VERSION_ID="9"' || "$VERSION_ID" = 'VERSION_ID="16.04"' || "$VERSION_ID" = 'VERSION_ID="17.04"' ]]; then
	nano /etc/squid/squid.conf
	exit
elif [[ "$VERSION_ID" = 'VERSION_ID="7"' || "$VERSION_ID" = 'VERSION_ID="8"' || "$VERSION_ID" = 'VERSION_ID="14.04"' ]]; then
	nano /etc/squid3/squid.conf
	exit
fi
	;;
	4)
nano /usr/local/bin/menu
exit
	;;

esac

	;;

	0) # ==================================================================================================================

rm -f /usr/local/bin/menu
wget -O /usr/local/bin/menu "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sernoomze/DeathSide-auto-script-Vpn/master/Menu"
chmod +x /usr/local/bin/menu
rm -f /usr/local/bin/Auto-Delete-Client 
wget -O /usr/local/bin/Auto-Delete-Client "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sernoomze/DeathSide-auto-script-Vpn/master/Auto-Delete-Client"
chmod +x /usr/local/bin/Auto-Delete-Client
menu

	;;

	00) # ==================================================================================================================

if [[ -e /usr/local/bin/Check-Thai ]]; then
	rm -f /usr/local/bin/Check-Thai
	menu
elif [[ ! -e /usr/local/bin/Check-Thai ]]; then
	echo "Check Thai" >> /usr/local/bin/Check-Thai
	menu
fi

	;;

esac
